Request Membership
Enjoy the Benefits of Dual Membership
Golf on a great Course with great people! Whether you’ve been golfing for years, or you have never held a club, KBCC has what you need. As a Kissimmee Bay member you can also enjoy playing privileges at our sister Course, Remington Golf Club, located only 1 mile from Kissimmee Bay.
Membership Options
Single Membership
Couples Membership
Family Membership
Benefits of Membership
Unlimited Play at BOTH Kissimmee Bay Country Club & Remington Golf Club
Two Weeks Advance Tee Time Booking Privileges
Charging Privileges (Monthly billing for anything that you want to charge to your account)
GHIN Handicapping service
10% OFF Pro Shop Merchandise at Both Kissimmee Bay & Remington
Special Member Pricing on Beer & Liquor
Participation in our Member Only Events Throughout the Year
Other Great Benefits
We take pride in having the finest 18 holes of golf in the area and providing golf leagues that players of all skill levels can enjoy. Kissimmee Bay Country Club & Remington Golf Club have numerous points and skins games happening throughout the week. Leagues for Men, Women, Couples, 18 holes, 9 holes; any type of league that you can imagine offering fun, casual, and competitive play.
Call us today to explore your membership
Call Kissimmee Bay Country Club for membership info at
(407) 348-4653
or fill out the form provided to request membership information.
